<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/WebPage">
<head>
    {{seo "Main" "slide4" "ZUBRY.BY - Private collection of postal items dedicated to the topic of bison. Posted by Artur Basak."}}
    {{resources true "slide4"}}

    <style>
        .skip-links {
            display: none;
        }

        .welcome {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 22px;
            z-index: 2;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 10% 16px 40px;
            max-width: 660px;
            width: 40%;

            font-family: var(--serif-fonts);
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 100;
            text-transform: inherit;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 6px #000;
            color: #fdfdfd;
        }

        .welcome h1 {
            position: unset;
            font-size: var(--welcome-head-text);
            margin-bottom: 0.75em;
            text-transform: unset;
        }

        .swiper-container {
            width: 100%;
            height: calc(100vh - 7.25em);
        }

        .swiper-slide {
            text-align: center;
            background-color: var(--black-color);
            background-position: center;
            background-size: cover;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .swiper-button-next,
        .swiper-button-prev {
            border-radius: 50%;
            height: 5em;
            width:  5em;
            outline: none;
        }

        .swiper-button-next:focus,
        .swiper-button-prev:focus {
            outline: 0.25em dotted white;
        }

        .swiper-pagination-bullet {
            width: 1em;
            height: 1em;
            opacity: 0.5;
            box-shadow: 0.2em 0.3em 0.8em var(--black-color);
        }

        .swiper-pagination-bullet:focus {
            outline: 0.25em dotted white;
        }

        .swiper-button-prev,
        .swiper-button-next {
            border: 0.3em solid var(--postcards-color);
        }

        .slide-0 {
            background-image:url(./assets/pics/slide0.jpg);
        }

        .slide-1 {
            background-image:url(./assets/pics/slide1.jpg);
        }

        .slide-2 {
            background-image:url(./assets/pics/slide2.jpg);
        }

        .slide-3 {
            background-image:url(./assets/pics/slide3.jpg);
        }

        .slide-4 {
            background-image:url(./assets/pics/slide4.jpg);
            background-position: top;
        }

        .slide-5 {
            background-image:url(./assets/pics/slide5.jpg);
            background-position: top;
        }

        @media (pointer: coarse) {
            .swiper-button-next:focus,
            .swiper-button-prev:focus,
            .swiper-pagination-bullet:focus {
                outline: none;
            }
        }


        @media (max-width: 800px) {
            :root {
                --head-1-text: 2rem
            }

            .welcome {
                top: initial;
                bottom: 0;
                left: 0;
                width: 100%;
                padding: 12px;
            }

            .swiper-container {
                width: 100%;
                height: calc(100vh - 7.25em);
            }

            .swiper-button-next,
            .swiper-button-prev {
                border: none;
            }

            .swiper-pagination {
                display: none;
            }

            .slide-0 {
                background-image:url(./assets/pics/slide0-800w.jpg);
            }

            .slide-1 {
                background-image:url(./assets/pics/slide1-800w.jpg);
            }

            .slide-2 {
                background-image:url(./assets/pics/slide2-800w.jpg);
            }

            .slide-3 {
                background-image:url(./assets/pics/slide3-800w.jpg);
            }

            .slide-4 {
                background-image:url(./assets/pics/slide4-800w.jpg);
            }

            .slide-5 {
                background-image:url(./assets/pics/slide5-800w.jpg);
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 400px) {
            .slide-0 {
                background-image:url(./assets/pics/slide0-400w.jpg);
            }

            .slide-1 {
                background-image:url(./assets/pics/slide1-400w.jpg);
            }

            .slide-2 {
                background-image:url(./assets/pics/slide2-400w.jpg);
            }

            .slide-3 {
                background-image:url(./assets/pics/slide3-400w.jpg);
            }

            .slide-4 {
                background-image:url(./assets/pics/slide4-400w.jpg);
            }

            .slide-5 {
                background-image:url(./assets/pics/slide5-400w.jpg);
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
{{header_en}}
<div class="swiper-container" id="content">
    <div class="welcome">
        <h1>Welcome to the Online Museum ZUBRY.BY</h1>
        <p>Данный сайт представляет собой каталог частной оцифрованной коллекции почтовых предметов, посвященных теме зубров.</p>
        <p>Начать осмотр -></p>
    </div>
    <div tabindex="0" role="region" aria-live="polite" class="swiper-wrapper">
        <div class="swiper-slide slide-1"></div>
        <div class="swiper-slide slide-5"></div>
        <div class="swiper-slide slide-2"></div>
        <div class="swiper-slide slide-0"></div>
        <div class="swiper-slide slide-3"></div>
        <div class="swiper-slide slide-4"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="swiper-pagination swiper-pagination-white"></div>
    <!--<div class="swiper-button-next swiper-button-white"></div>-->
    <!--<div class="swiper-button-prev swiper-button-white"></div>-->
</div>
{{footer_en}}
</body>
</html>
